'''Zumrud Gulu-zade''' ({{lang-az|Zümrüd Qulu-zadə}}) ({{IPA-tr|zym'ɾyt gulu'zɑdæ}}; is an [[Azerbaijani (people)|Azerbaijani]] professor of philosophy at the [[Azerbaijan National Academy of Sciences]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://az.apa.az/news.php?id=52687|title=Sənətşünaslıq elmləri doktoru Zümrüd Quluzadənin 75 yaşı qeyd olunacaq|date=27 March 2007|work=APA.az|language=Azerbaijani|accessdate=27 July 2011}}</ref>
Zumrud Gulu-zade has written many books on philosophy in the [[Azerbaijani (language)|Azerbaijanian]], [[Turkish (language)|Turkish]], [[English (language)|English]] and [[Russian (language)|Russian]] languages.
